title: "LexiMus-UR: Melcior 1859 chord ontology model"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-03-31"
repository-code: "https://github.com/LexiMusUR/Melcior1859"
license: CC-BY-4.0
keywords:
  - music ontology
  - historical music dictionary
  - propositional analysis
  - CIDOC-CRM
  - knowledge representation
  - Melcior 1859
  - Spanish music lexicography
abstract: >
  Formal ontology model of the chord entry in Carlos José Melcior's
  Diccionario enciclopédico de la música (Lérida, 1859), developed
  through propositional analysis anchored in CIDOC-CRM. The model
  comprises 1,328 triples, 71 classes, and 37 properties covering
  normative, evaluative, perceptual, and epistemic content absent
  from current music ontologies.
